mented-generation-RAG#:~:text=RAG%20has%20additional%20benefits,%E2%80%98hallucinate%E2%80%99%20incorrect%20or%20misleading%20information","line":11},{"title":"What is retrieval-augmented generation (RAG)? - IBM Research","target":"https://research.ibm.com/blog/retrieval-augmented-generation-RAG#:~:text=Retrieval,LLM%E2%80%99s%20internal%20representation%20of%20information","line":11},{"title":"What is retrieval-augmented generation (RAG)? - IBM Research","target":"https://research.ibm.com/blog/retrieval-augmented-generation-RAG#:~:text=Retrieval,LLM%E2%80%99s%20internal%20representation%20of%20information","line":11},{"title":"A Graph-Based Approach for Conversational AI-Driven Personal Memory Capture and Retrieval in a Real-world Application","target":"https://arxiv.org/html/2412.05447v1#:~:text=create%20a%20dynamic%20knowledge%20graph,retrieval%20accuracy%20and%20reduced%20hallucination","line":15},{"title":"A Graph-Based Approach for Conversational AI-Driven Personal Memory Capture and Retrieval in a Real-world Application","target":"https://arxiv.org/html/2412.05447v1#:~:text=generation%20,and%20recall%2C%20significantly%20improving%20user","line":15},{"title":"Zep: A Temporal Knowledge Graph Architecture for Agent Memory","target":"https://blog.getzep.com/zep-a-temporal-knowledge-graph-architecture-for-agent-memory/#:~:text=limitation%20through%20its%20core%20component,while%20simultaneously%20reducing","line":15},{"title":"Zep: A Temporal Knowledge Graph Architecture for Agent Memory","target":"https://blog.getzep.com/zep-a-temporal-knowledge-graph-architecture-for-agent-memory/#:~:text=metric%2C%20Zep%20demonstrates%20superior%20performance,world%20applications","line":15}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
